                            <comment id="13087927" author="karthick" created="Fri, 19 Aug 2011 20:05:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;To address the leak described above, I feel that we should explicitly remove the &lt;tt&gt;HTableInstance&lt;/tt&gt; to be released from the &lt;tt&gt;PoolMap&lt;/tt&gt;. And, for good measure, we should clear the &lt;tt&gt;PoolMap&lt;/tt&gt; when the &lt;tt&gt;HTablePool&lt;/tt&gt; is closed. Please review the corresponding patch, which passes all unit tests.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
